{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_9", "eventName": "風暴瞭望", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "9-12", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "鬼影如潮", "storyInfo": "城中受髒彈轟炸，死傷慘重，羅德島幹員決定在撤離前對當地居民實施救援，簡加入了救援隊伍。風笛見信使已死，決定穿越城區，回去找號角。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G9_rhodes_xqoffice", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#4", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大家都沒事吧？", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#4"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_013_riop", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多虧了您提醒，我們都及時躲起來了......咳咳咳，小簡妮，你呢，還好嗎？", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我很好，Outcast完全護住了我。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是外面......發生了什麼？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽到很多人在慘叫......還有孩子們......", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#4"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "簡，你還不能出去！所有人，繼續趴在掩體附近，盡可能遠離門窗！", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#4"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這種規模的轟炸不會只有一波——", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#4"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_explo_n"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.8, "xstrength": 50.0, "ystrength": 50.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊啊啊！我、我的腿......被書架壓住了......", "name": "幹員弗雷德"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#4"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "威爾，幫弗雷德一把！", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#4"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_090", "name2": "char_empty", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈......謝謝，兄弟，我現在能動了。", "name": "幹員弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#4"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有沒有流血？", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#4"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心，只有一點點。", "name": "幹員弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#4"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "醫療包還在嗎？拿出急性感染前期阻斷劑，立刻服下去！", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#4"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？女士，我只是小腿上的皮被木頭劃破了一塊，連骨頭都沒傷到。", "name": "幹員弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，你錯了。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你現在正處於最高級別的感染風險中——看到那塊扎破窗戶的黑色結晶了嗎？", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天、天呐......我......", "name": "幹員弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......這是活性源石？！", "name": "幹員碎紙機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_089"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道說，街上那些黑漆漆的......全部都是？！", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恐怕是的。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......我不敢相信......", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_013_riop"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這、這豈不是說全城都暴露在巨大的危險中？", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "該死！女士，我們必須儘快對附近的人們進行緊急救援！時間緊迫，能救一個是一個！", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其他人有意見嗎？", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我本來以為有意見的會是奧利弗。", "name": "幹員碎紙機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_089"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_013_riop"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都什麼時候了，你還挖苦我！趕緊去收拾急救包啊！弗雷德受傷了，原地待命，負責我們之間的聯絡！威爾，你趕緊回去看看你的父母——", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_090"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也可以和大家一起......", "name": "幹員威爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_090"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_013_riop"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別糊塗了！工作有親人重要？帶上足量的藥，救完你家人，順便把你那一條街的鄰居都好好檢查一下！", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_090"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老大，謝謝......", "name": "幹員威爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_090"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_013_riop"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "碎紙機，老朋友，我們得多跑幾條街了。", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "char_013_riop", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別忘了我，奧利弗，我現在也算你手下的臨時幹員。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "char_013_riop", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女士，您別開玩笑了。", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "char_013_riop", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說正經的，第十區附近交給我。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "char_013_riop", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那裡是轟炸中心，最危險......", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "char_013_riop", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不然呢？也請給我一個臨時通訊器，我們隨時互相通報進度。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "各位，我也想一起......", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_013_riop"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，小簡妮，這救援任務不是開玩笑的，你不像我們這樣受過專業訓練，沒必要冒這險。", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說到底，誰出的狠毒主意，往人堆裡丟活性源石？這都是那幫*維多利亞粗口*暴徒幹的？！", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能在極短時間內對這麼廣的區域狂轟濫炸，策劃這場襲擊的人，至少投入了超過十門最先進的地面壓制榴彈炮。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼多火炮......", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我遠遠看過這兩天的戰鬥。那些被你們稱作暴徒的人，他們之中有著很強的術師，這給部隊帶來了一定隱匿能力。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——可還遠遠沒到能讓他們帶著這麼多高殺傷性武器進城，且不被駐軍發現的地步。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更何況，他們還不至於蠢到用炮口對準好不容易搶下的城區，把當地居民連帶著自己人炸得支離破碎吧？", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您、您的意思是......", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "簡，你知道答案。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.8}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，這不可能......", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您是想說，我們的人炮轟了城區？！是我們......殺死了這麼多平民，還謀劃著將數量更多的平民拖入礦石病的深淵？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#5"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是駐軍。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#5"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "駐軍明白這場仗贏不了，因為塔拉出身的人們都在幫另一邊。既然無法區分誰才是奸細，他們決定索性將敵人連同平民一網打盡——", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#5"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而使用髒彈，正是為了絕後患。所有礦石病患者都會被集中管理，這給了駐軍藉口，他們之後將能堂而皇之地清理塔拉人。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#5"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是......把人命看作取勝的手段？維多利亞的軍隊，不該保護維多利亞人嗎？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你很激動，我理解，這正是由於你擁有一顆許多士兵缺乏的仁慈之心。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "過去幾百年間，維多利亞軍隊碾過這片大地上的無數國家與人群，靠的可從來不是仁慈。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難怪，在塔拉居民眼裡，暴徒們會是正義的......", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都是只想著利用無辜者性命、為自己謀求利益的組織，不同花樣的面具下是同樣醜惡麻木的面孔，又有什麼區別？", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼——是不是只有羅德島在做對的事？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你有多麼瞭解羅德島？", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我信任著奧利弗叔叔他們，而且，從我認識您的第一天起，我就一直信任著您......", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#2$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#5"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你對我，又瞭解多少？", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#5"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_013_riop"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女士，您何必這麼嚴肅，小簡妮她需要一點時間來接受......", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......沒關係，奧利弗叔叔，我明白Outcast的意思。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我確實......很感激你們收留了無處可去的我。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也確實，我仍在迷茫......每當我決定站在哪一邊的時候，總有人告訴我，我不屬於那一邊。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但至少在這一刻，我明白自己該做什麼。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請讓我和你們一起行動。我要盡可能地幫助外面那些受傷的人。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即使，他們中的一部分，剛剛還在朝你丟石頭、趕你走？", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#7"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就跟您說的那樣，我始終無法對惡行袖手旁觀——這和我選擇站在哪裡沒有關係。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奧利弗，你聽到了？你是小丘郡辦事處的負責人，你同意簡·薇洛的臨時加入嗎？", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_013_riop"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我、我沒意見！", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正好急救品都收拾好了，小簡妮，你想和誰一塊行動都行。", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我也去中央城區。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_013_riop"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，那就是和Outcast女士一塊？呼，我還以為經過剛才那一齣，你會有些怕她......", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#2"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#2"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_013_riop"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我什麼都沒說！", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然準備好了，大家就各自出發吧。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "記住，保護自己是第一位的——你們既需要做好大面積污染源面前的防護，也需要儘量躲避潛在的敵人。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，以目前的情況來看，無論是哪方士兵，都有可能是我們的敵人。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G4_victoria_street_d_ruins"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rainheavy_loop", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "廚子先生，廚子先生——", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，怎麼辦，到處都是傷患。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_explo_n", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_imp_rock_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳咳，咳咳咳......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#6"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不行，我一定要找到廚子先生，他應該就在這附近，我必須把他護送出城！", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#6"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......欸，什麼東西抓住了我的小腿？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_244"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_244"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是......敵人？！", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——！", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，你已經喪失了行動能力。我不該再對你動手。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_244"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......殺了......我......", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_244"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先別說話，我幫你把壓著腿的這塊石頭抬起來再說。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#6"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿哈——", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#6"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了！唉，都壓爛了啊，而且......這些黑色的結晶......看起來好嚴重。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_244"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "殺了......我！", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_244"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不能......感染者......骯髒......玷污！", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_244"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#6"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還說這種話做什麼？努力活下來不好嗎？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#6"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_244"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你......不懂......", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_244"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這比死......更可怕......", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_244"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說我不懂就不懂吧。我還要去找人，沒辦法救你了。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#6"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "廚子先生！廚子——", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#6"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_244"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵......", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_244"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你又拉我做什麼？這......這條圍裙！廚子先生——！", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（這塊石頭，原來還壓在了廚子先生身上。難怪我沒能找到他。）", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（情報都還在。）", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（看得出來，最後一刻，廚子先生拼盡全力護住了這些重要的證據。）", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "麥克馬丁先生，雖然我也許並不知道您的真名——但我會記住您做的事。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安息吧，我的戰友。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不會讓你的英勇白費。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有你。我也要謝謝你，不知名的敵人。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我本該答應你最後的請求，但我看得出來，不需要我動手，你已經快死了。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還有什麼話想說嗎？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_244"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......領袖。", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_244"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到這時候，你心裡依舊只想著領袖？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_244"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈......哈哈哈哈！", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_244"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們......即將......迎來......新生之火！", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_244"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在看什——", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "越來越多的敵人正踏著廢墟湧來。"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "敵人的援軍到了？！", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "炮轟根本沒有起到正面作用......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隊長......隊長他們會有危險！", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我必須和他們會合——", 